    Update Sample Location

    update_sample_location.Rd

    update_sample_location() updates an existing sample location in the sample location lookup table

    update_sample_location(con, sample_location_id, sample_location)

    Arguments

    con

    A DBI connection object obtained from DBI::dbConnect()

    sample_location_id

    A numeric ID for the targeted sample location get_sample_locations

    sample_location

    A valid sample location dataframe with the following:

    1. code character A short code for the agency

    2. agency_name character The agency's proper name

    See also

    Other sample location functions: add_sample_location(), delete_sample_location(), get_sample_locations(), update_sample_location_status()
